[
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0001",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "h1",
    "text": "Transitioning to mainstream Lean",
    "html": "<h1>Transitioning to mainstream Lean<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#transitioning-to-mainstream-lean\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\"></a></h1>",
    "zh": "过渡到主流 Lean"
  },
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0002",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "If you have enjoyed this book, you may wish to work further with Lean, for example by working through the book Mathematics in Lean or by starting an independent formalization project .",
    "html": "<p>If you have enjoyed this book, you may wish to work further with Lean, for example by working\nthrough the book\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathematics_in_lean/\">Mathematics in Lean</a> or by starting\nan\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/wiki/Using-mathlib4-as-a-dependency\">independent formalization project</a>.</p>",
    "zh": "如果你喜欢本书，也许会希望进一步使用 Lean，例如阅读 <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathematics_in_lean/\">Mathematics in Lean</a>，或启动一个独立的形式化项目。"
  },
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0003",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "You will discover that the Lean “dialect” used in this book differs from the mainstream mathematical Lean used in the library mathlib and its associated literature such as Mathematics in Lean . To help you adjust, in this appendix I outline the major differences.",
    "html": "<p>You will discover that the Lean “dialect” used in this book differs from the mainstream mathematical\nLean used in the library <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4\">mathlib</a> and its\nassociated literature such as <em>Mathematics in Lean</em>.  To help you adjust, in this appendix I outline\nthe major differences.</p>",
    "zh": "你会发现，本书使用的 Lean“方言”不同于 mathlib 库及其相关文献（例如 Mathematics in Lean）中使用的主流数学 Lean。为了帮助你适应，本附录概述主要差异。"
  },
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0004",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "Some tactics used in this book are deliberately weakened versions of tactics in mathlib: I have done this to block certain of Lean’s capabilities because prose proofs at the level of this book would typically write out the details in full. These deliberately weakened tactics include:",
    "html": "<p>Some tactics used in this book are deliberately weakened versions of tactics in mathlib: I have\ndone this to block certain of Lean’s capabilities because prose proofs at the level of this book\nwould typically write out the details in full. These deliberately weakened tactics include:</p>",
    "zh": "本书中使用的一些策略，是 mathlib 中相应策略的有意弱化版本。我这样做，是为了屏蔽 Lean 的某些能力，因为在本书层次的文字证明中，通常会把这些细节完整写出。这些有意弱化的策略包括："
  },
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0005",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "mathlib tactic",
    "html": "<p>mathlib tactic</p>",
    "zh": "mathlib 策略"
