    "text": "Some tactics used in this book have no mathlib analogues. They are typically wrappers for a small collection of lemmas, and in mathlib these lemmas would be invoked by name.",
    "html": "<p>Some tactics used in this book have no mathlib analogues.  They are typically wrappers for a small\ncollection of lemmas, and in mathlib these lemmas would be invoked by name.</p>",
