  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0059",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "Another point not covered in this book is how to interact with the library. Since mathlib contains over a million lines of Lean code, it is not always easy to find out whether a lemma you want exists in the library! In this book, I avoid the issue by telling you in advance the name of any lemma I expect you to use.",
    "html": "<p>Another point not covered in this book is how to interact with the library.  Since mathlib contains\nover a million lines of Lean code, it is not always easy to find out whether a lemma you want exists\nin the library!  In this book, I avoid the issue by telling you in advance the name of any lemma I\nexpect you to use.</p>",
    "zh": "本书没有涉及的另一点，是如何与库交互。由于 mathlib 含有超过一百万行 Lean 代码，要弄清库中是否已经有你想要的引理，并不总是容易的。本书通过预先告诉你希望你使用的每个引理名称来避开这个问题。"
  },
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0060",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "A few basic points to be aware of in interacting with the library:",
    "html": "<p>A few basic points to be aware of in interacting with the library:</p>",
    "zh": "与库交互时，需要了解以下几个基本点："
  },
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0061",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "p",
    "text": "All this only scratches the surface: there are many more features of Lean to help you in your mathematical discoveries. Mathematics in Lean , the community website , and the community discussion board offer further pointers for exploration. Have fun!",
    "html": "<p>All this only scratches the surface: there are many more features of Lean to help you in your\nmathematical discoveries.  <em>Mathematics in Lean</em>, the\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/\">community website</a>, and the\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://leanprover.zulipchat.com/\">community discussion board</a> offer further pointers for\nexploration.  Have fun!</p>",
    "zh": "以上只是触及皮毛：Lean 还有许多更多功能，可以帮助你进行数学探索。<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathematics_in_lean/\">Mathematics in Lean</a>、<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/\">社区网站</a>和<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://leanprover.zulipchat.com/\">社区讨论区</a>提供了进一步探索的指引。祝你玩得开心！"
  },
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0062",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "li",
    "text": "The online documentation is generally more readable than the source code: it is searchable and it has internal hyperlinks.",
    "html": "<li><p>The <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/\">online documentation</a> is generally\nmore readable than the source code: it is searchable and it has internal hyperlinks.</p></li>",
    "zh": "在线文档通常比源代码更易读：它可搜索，并且含有内部超链接。"
  },
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0063",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "li",
    "text": "Lemmas are often stated in extreme generality … \\((a - b) + c = a - (b - c)\\) is stated not for \\(\\mathbb{R}\\) but for a SubtractionCommMonoid . You may have better luck interacting with the library after first courses on abstract algebra and point-set topology.",
    "html": "<li><p>Lemmas are often stated in extreme generality … <span class=\"math notranslate nohighlight\">\\((a - b) + c = a - (b - c)\\)</span>\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Basic.html#sub_sub\">is stated</a>\nnot for <span class=\"math notranslate nohighlight\">\\(\\mathbb{R}\\)</span> but for a <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">SubtractionCommMonoid</span></code>.  You may have better\nluck interacting with the library after first courses on abstract algebra and point-set topology.</p></li>",
    "zh": "引理往往以极高的一般性陈述……\\((a - b) + c = a - (b - c)\\) 不是针对 \\(\\mathbb{R}\\) 陈述的，而是针对 SubtractionCommMonoid 陈述的。在修完抽象代数和点集拓扑的第一门课程之后，你可能会更容易与库交互。"
  },
  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0064",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "li",
    "text": "If you can guess the exact statement of a lemma, the tactic exact? will find it in the library.",
    "html": "<li><p>If you can guess the exact statement of a lemma, the tactic <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">exact?</span></code> will find it in the\nlibrary.</p></li>",
    "zh": "如果你能猜出一个引理的精确陈述，策略 exact? 会在库中找到它。"
  },
