  {
    "id": "Mainstream_Lean:0081",
    "file": "Mainstream_Lean.html",
    "tag": "td",
    "text": "linarith can take constant multiples of linear inequalities as well as adding/subtracting constants, it can combine many linear inequalities, and it does not require you to state which hypotheses you are using",
    "html": "<td><p><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">linarith</span></code> can take constant multiples of linear inequalities as well</p>\n<p>as adding/subtracting constants, it can combine many linear</p>\n<p>inequalities, and it does not require you to state which hypotheses</p>\n<p>you are using</p>\n</td>",
    "zh": "linarith 除了加减常数外，还可以取线性不等式的常数倍；它能组合许多线性不等式，而且不要求你说明正在使用哪些假设"
  },
